  ECHO PLAYER Sawing away at the violin, you produce a lively melody perfect for dancing to.
  ECHO OTHERS %N saws away at the violin, producing a lively melody perfect for dancing to.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER Don't you think having it in your hands might help?
  ENDIF
ENDIF
