;
; Watch
INUMBER 1199
NAME 928
VARIABLE WATCH
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
MISC
CRAFTABLE
ENCRUSTABLE
WORN_WRIST
SUBSTANCE SOFTMETAL
PARAMETER2 29
IFVERB READ -1
  ECHO OTHERS %N glances at %h watch.
  EQUAL WATCH TIM
  IFVAR WATCH = 12
    ECHO PLAYER it is around noon.
  ELSE
    IFVAR WATCH > 12
      SUB WATCH 12
      STRCVT 0 WATCH
      ECHO PLAYER it is around %0:00 PM.
    ELSE
      STRCVT 0 WATCH
      ECHO PLAYER it is around %0:00 AM.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
*DESCRIPTION_START READ
The watch isn't that accurate, but your best estimate indicates that
*DESCRIPTION_END
